lead_paragraph: Venus Williams avoided another early exit with a routine win over fellow American Alison Riske at the Volvo Car Open in South Carolina while Swiss second seed Belinda Bencic was ousted by Russian qualifier Elena Vesnina.

headline.print_headline: Venus Powers on, Bencic Upset in Charleston
